extends ../../layout

block style
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/lib/swiper/css/swiper.min.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/css/my.swiper.css')
block content
  include ../../component/navbar.pug
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-3
        include ../component/menu.pug
      .col-md-9
        h2 setWrapperSize
        p Seiper从3.0开始使用flexbox布局(display:flex)，开启这个设定会再Wrapper上添加等于slides相加的宽度，在对flexbox布局的支持不是很好的浏览器中可能需要用到。
        h4 setWrapperSize参数
        p 类型：<span class="label label-info">boolean</span> 默认：<span class="label label-info">false</span> 举例：<span class="label label-info">true</span> 启用版本：<span class="label label-info">3.0.6</span>
        h4 效果演示
        .desc
          p 审查元素查看Wrapper的style
          .swiper-container#e1
            .swiper-wrapper
              .swiper-slide slider1
              .swiper-slide slider2
              .swiper-slide slider3
block script
  script(src="/lib/swiper/js/swiper.jquery.min.js")
  script(src="/js/my.swiper.js")
  script.
    $(function() {
      var e1 = new Swiper('#e1', {
        setWrapperSize: true,
      })
    })